@host = {{host}}
@token = {{token}}
@userId = {{userId}}
@compartmentIdAlt = {{compartmentIdAlt}}

### Quitar compartimento — path anidado
# `{compartment_id}` es el FK de compartimento, no la fila pivote interna.

DELETE {{host}}/api/v1/user-authorizations/{{userId}}/compartments/{{compartmentIdAlt}}/
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
